data.description: This 4 bed 2 1/2 bath with addition sits on an oversized lot, down a quiet dead end road right in the middle of town. Spacious Den and Living with loft, and a wood burning fireplace for those cooler nights coming. Kitchen offers Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Countertops, and Breakfast Bar, with separate dining area. Primary Bedroom features high ceilings with double vanity sinks, garden tub and separate stand up shower. Enjoy your inground salt water pool out back with a cabana and bathroom with changing area that has electric and water ran to it. Backyard also has a shed with Lime, Lemon, and Fig trees, rear yard access, with camper hookups and camper storage on the side of the home. Extra amenities include work out room with cedar sauna and office area off the kitchen. This one is a must see!
